Title: Cloud Fishing
Description:
Now that we have the eels, we can try to lure the cloudrooks back to land. 

Head over to the neighboring island. Get as close as you can and make an offering to the rooks. 

With luck, they'll cease their circling and come down for a nourishing meal.
ObjectivesText: Offer 8 Electric Eels to Wild Cloudrooks.
CompletionText: Nothing better than electric eels to sate a tired and hungry cloudrook.
RewardText:
Now I understand. This is how the rooks bring their own over from the elemental plane. They weren't mourning so much as calling out to their departed kin.

Thank you for your help, outlander. You've helped me better understand these beautiful creatures.
